	(333,269,'summary','The Anchor Program serves local communities by offering exposure to viable career choices for young adults, and others, whose options may be limited. We provide a lifestyle alternative through training, certification, and preparation for a career in the growing maritime industry where graduates have the potential to earn a substantial salary, travel the world, and create a new career path.'),
