	(20,1,'2015-02-13 10:42:29','2015-02-13 10:42:29','<p>Upon completion of our program, our graduates are fully prepared to begin a career in the Merchant Marine. Our advisors work hard to provide any advice, resources, and/or recommendations necessary to aid our graduates in their process and we take pride in ushering new Mariners into their career at sea.</p>','Basic Maritime Training','','publish','closed','closed','','basic-maritime-training','','','2015-02-13 12:13:11','2015-02-13 12:13:11','',0,'http://dev.tap.local/?post_type=course_page&#038;p=20',0,'course_page','',0),
