	(261,1,'2013-08-06 21:13:59','2013-08-06 21:13:59','Our next Basic Program training class will begin August 15th in Richmond, CA. Participants will receive a combination of online training and 8 weeks of hands on training aboard the SS Red Oak Victory.\n\n<a class=\"read-more\" style=\"float: none;\" title=\"Basic Maritime Training\" href=\"http://www.theanchorprogram.com/course/basic-maritime-training/\">Learn more about our Basic Program</a>','Basic Maritime Training Program: Next Class August 15th, Richmond CA','','publish','open','open','','hello-world-2','','','2013-08-06 21:13:59','2013-08-06 21:13:59','',0,'http://www.theanchorprogram.com/?p=1',0,'post','',0),
